{"tid":1056802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突破資訊封鎖  問爆陳茂波","createTime":"2019-03-11T12:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T00:05:31.000Z","uid":138409,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d2d2397e5cff31c4b794c5d79a8a94c2e31b01","tid":1056802,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T12:21:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/photos/a.326590167437063/2219116641517730/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2Fphotos%2Fa.326590167437063%2F2219116641517730%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=0c1c6a63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/photos/a.326590167437063/2219116641517730/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n從事民間研究嘅最大困難就係缺乏研究資料。好多有爭議性嘅政策，政府都會迴避向公眾交代細節。<br />\n<br />\n例如去年土地大辯論，政府連最基本嘅土地、規劃數據都唔交代清楚，然後搏大家唔知，強推自己想推嘅政策（如萬億人工島同公私合營發展農地）。<br />\n<br />\n類似情況不但出現係土地政策方面、各項影響民生嘅政策，例如城市規劃、房屋、社福、醫療、食物安全等等，都有以上「唔清唔楚」嘅狀況，資訊封鎖窒礙民間、以至學術界從事政策研究，到頭來管治質素惡化，受害嘅係每個香港人。<br />\n<br />\n為咗扭轉呢個狀態，本土研究社連續第三年同立法會議員合作，係嚟緊審議財政預算案嘅「特別財務委員會」會議，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">炮製咗256條尖銳嘅政策問題</span></span>，交俾立法會議員要求政府全面交代。呢個行動除咗能夠迫政府停止「唧牙膏」外，仲提供極大量最新政策資料，幫助議員議政之餘，亦提供極寶貴嘅政策資料作民間研究。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x5LF7gN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx5LF7gN.jpg&h=1370cbb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢256條問題，涵蓋土地、城市規劃、房屋、社福醫療， 以至中港關係、檔案法、資訊自由法等等不同急需加強民間同議會監察嘅政策範疇，實行「問爆財仔波」－今年政府洗咗幾多錢落研究大灣區跨境基建？各項中港跨境合作、人才入境計劃詳情為何？未來有否計劃改善公私營醫療失衡？未來綠置居政策會否侵蝕公共房屋資源？<br />\n<br />\n第一輪256條問題已經全數交俾5位立法會議員代為質問政府，為進一步加強「公眾參與」，<span style=\"color: gold;\">我哋現在向大家收集更多政策問題（inbox 我哋）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2F&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=fd82c8c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/</a><br />\n，題材不拘，但最好係政府多年「唧牙膏」嘅政策範疇</span>，如果適合的話，我哋會提交比議員在次輪「特別財務委員會」補充問題環節（今年四至五月）代為質問政府，咁樣先係真正嘅「公眾參與」呀嘛！<br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n一齊打爆波叔<br />\n💪了解更多: <a href=\"http://liber-research.com/about-us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fabout-us&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=019cf4f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://liber-research.com/about-us</a><br />\n💰支持我們: <a href=\"http://liber-research.com/support-us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fsupport-us&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=c6ff6fa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://liber-research.com/support-us</a>"},{"pid":"8d0023700d0cd569c4fe6ac911663d7164fae101","tid":1056802,"uid":173599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T12:38:32.000Z","msg":"點睇劏房?<br />\n點睇醉駕?<br />\n呀荗你都係返去整餅啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fb5f85e4fddf2594342bb1147f189568de6064","tid":1056802,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:19:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d0d160ca4dffc5011a7d220bde19f35221c4640b","tid":1056802,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:24:30.000Z","msg":"外匯基金/儲備 有幾多買左一帶一路/大陸資產/人民弊 ???"},{"pid":"56655b4f68e35c60da7a2210f526dff06783ba1b","tid":1056802,"uid":121246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:31:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7d7e28bb55b9e7f34634378c8b34e9544e8b8c1","tid":1056802,"uid":37358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:42:57.000Z","msg":"其實sfc q 有好多部門比啲info係唔準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e62e30847a8e93fc91e8d8e40a4481f7afabf46","tid":1056802,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:24:5